# OCI Generative AI Agent Hands-On Lab Project

This is a hands-on lab project for learning Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI) Generative AI Agents. The project demonstrates building AI agents for hotel concierge services using OCI's Agent Development Kit (ADK).

## Project Structure

- **Main entry point**: [main.py](mdc:main.py) - Simple entry point for the project
- **Project configuration**: [pyproject.toml](mdc:pyproject.toml) - Python project dependencies and metadata
- **Main documentation**: [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Comprehensive setup and usage guide
- **Lab modules**: [labs/](mdc:labs/) - Contains individual lab exercises

## Lab Structure

### Lab 1: Basic Review Analysis

- **Location**: [labs/lab-1/](mdc:labs/lab-1/)
- **Purpose**: Individual review analysis in multiple languages
- **Key files**: [labs/lab-1/README.md](mdc:labs/lab-1/README.md)

### Lab 2: Advanced Agentic Concierge

- **Location**: [labs/lab-2/](mdc:labs/lab-2/)
- **Purpose**: Building a comprehensive hotel concierge agent with RAG and web search capabilities
- **Key files**:
  - [labs/lab-2/README.md](mdc:labs/lab-2/README.md) - Detailed lab instructions
  - [labs/lab-2/concierge_agent.py](mdc:labs/lab-2/concierge_agent.py) - Main agent implementation
  - [labs/lab-2/test.py](mdc:labs/lab-2/test.py) - Authentication and debugging tests
  - [labs/lab-2/setup.py](mdc:labs/lab-2/setup.py) - Setup automation

## Datasets

- **Location**: [labs/datasets/](mdc:labs/datasets/)
- **Content**: TripAdvisor multi-language hotel reviews
- **Formats**: CSV and Markdown versions for different use cases

## Key Technologies

- **OCI Generative AI Agents**: Core AI agent platform
- **OCI ADK (Agent Development Kit)**: Python SDK for building agents
- **RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation)**: Knowledge base integration
- **Web Search Tools**: Real-time internet information retrieval
- **Multi-language Support**: Vietnamese, Chinese, Korean, and English reviews

## Use Case: Hotel Concierge Agent

The project demonstrates building an AI concierge for the Grand Plaza Hotel in Ho Chi Minh City that can:

- Analyze guest reviews in multiple languages
- Identify patterns across thousands of reviews
- Search the internet for real-time information
- Provide proactive guest service solutions
